<div style="padding-top:300px; width:600px;">

Drop chance of grade 1 monster. Grade2+ gives really higher dropchance. Grade 6+ drops almost always only items.<br>
"medicine" Drop chance: 30%  ; 1 from 3<br>
"gold" Drop chance: 21%  ; 1 from 5    <br>
"<span style='font-weight:bold;color:gray;'>weak helmet</span>"   	Drop chance: 24.5%  ; 1 from 4<br>
"<span style='font-weight:bold;color:green;'>normal helmet</span>"    	Drop chance: 20.43% ; 1 from 5<br>
"<span style='font-weight:bold;color:blue;'>good helmet</span>"    		Drop chance: 3.39% ; 1 from 30<br>
"<span style='font-weight:bold;color:purple;'>very good helmet</span>"          Drop chance: 0.563% ; 1 from 178<br>
"<span style='font-weight:bold;color:red;'>super good helmet</span>"         Drop chance: 0.093% ; 1 from 1075<br>
"<span style='font-weight:bold;color:#ec27e5;'>insane helmet</span>"             Drop chance: 0.0155% ; 1 from 6451<br>
"<span style='font-weight:bold;color:orange;'>super insane helmet</span>"       Drop chance: 0.00305% ; 1 from 28571<br>
<br><br>
If your HP is less than 10%, you can't attack any monster.<br>
After attacking you need wait 2 seconds before attacking again. <br>
If you are using an item, you need to "Out" it to use another item.<br>
You can use medicine every 5 seconds.<br>
Your inventory is unlimited.<br>
When you get enough exp press the level up button.<br>
You can use item if your level is not lower than items level.<br>
Every 10 levels you have new medicine with more HP regeneration.<br>
Every 50 agility your crit chance is +1%<br>
Every 500 agility your critical multiplier is +1<br>
